      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2024-01-24T19:08:54.384Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes I was saying Zwift might do this.  Compare how long it takes from the time target is sent to the time the trainer adjusts the watts.  This part of our code is already very complex and my personal belief is being off by a second or two is not critical to training but I am also not the one experiencing this.  We have not changed this code in 4 years and you guys are the first ones saying anything out of like 20,000 user that have used our app so people with similar delays, I would assume just accept it.</p>\n<p>I realized if I could just see a screen shot, you should see it.  If there is a delay and the power is happening after the target.   Super short workouts like 2 minutes it\u2019s super obvious but since most people are doing longer workouts then it\u2019s not so obvious.</p>\n<p>Below you can see my trainer on super short workout.  It\u2019s slightly delayed but it does not actually affect the workout.  And long workouts you don\u2019t really see it.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5_2_485x500.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"1FDtxBKmuIWwAjfzUTmJUvS0Jhj\" width=\"485\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5_2_485x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5_2_727x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85a19bcf64c4ae5_2_970x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0bb711c20b939bb81eb790a0d85